# =============================================================================
# Web Research Tool - API Configuration
# =============================================================================
# 
# This tool implements a 6-tier CAPTCHA-resistant search strategy.
# Configure as many of these as possible for maximum reliability.
#
# Priority order (highest to lowest):
# 1. SERPAPI_KEY - Google search results without CAPTCHA ($50/month)
# 2. BRAVE_API_KEY - Fast, reliable, $5 free credits/month
# 3. BING_API_KEY - Microsoft search API (free tier available)
# 4. GOOGLE_CSE_API_KEY + GOOGLE_CSE_ID - Google Custom Search
# 5. SCRAPINGBEE_KEY - Premium proxy service for hard-to-scrape sites
# 6. DuckDuckGo - Free fallback (may encounter CAPTCHA)
#
# The more providers you configure, the more resilient your searches become.

# -----------------------------------------------------------------------------
# TIER 1: SerpAPI (Recommended - handles Google without CAPTCHA)
# Get your key at: https://serpapi.com/
# Pricing: $50/month for 5,000 searches (no CAPTCHA issues)
# -----------------------------------------------------------------------------
SERPAPI_KEY=your_serpapi_key_here

# -----------------------------------------------------------------------------
# TIER 2: Brave Search API (Fast, reliable, good free tier)
# Get your key at: https://api.search.brave.com/
# Pricing: $5 free credits/month, then pay-as-you-go
# -----------------------------------------------------------------------------
BRAVE_API_KEY=your_brave_api_key_here

# -----------------------------------------------------------------------------
# TIER 3: Bing Search API (Microsoft alternative)
# Get your key at: https://www.microsoft.com/en-us/bing/apis/bing-web-search-api
# Pricing: 1,000 queries/month free, then $7 per 1,000 queries
# -----------------------------------------------------------------------------
BING_API_KEY=your_bing_api_key_here

# -----------------------------------------------------------------------------
# TIER 4: Google Custom Search Engine (CSE)
# Get your API key: https://developers.google.com/custom-search/v1/overview
# Create your CSE: https://cse.google.com/cse/create
# Pricing: 100 queries/day free, then $5 per 1,000 queries
# -----------------------------------------------------------------------------
GOOGLE_CSE_API_KEY=your_google_api_key_here
GOOGLE_CSE_ID=your_custom_search_engine_id_here

# -----------------------------------------------------------------------------
# TIER 5: ScrapingBee (Premium proxy for hard-to-scrape sites)
# Get your key at: https://www.scrapingbee.com/
# Pricing: Starting at $49/month for 100,000 API credits
# -----------------------------------------------------------------------------
SCRAPINGBEE_KEY=your_scrapingbee_key_here

# -----------------------------------------------------------------------------
# OPTIONAL: Google AI API (alternative to GOOGLE_CSE_API_KEY)
# If GOOGLE_CSE_API_KEY is not set, the tool will try GOOGLE_AI_API_KEY
# -----------------------------------------------------------------------------
GOOGLE_AI_API_KEY=your_google_ai_api_key_here
